data.description: Welcome Home  to this  4 Bedroom, One Of A Kind, Colonial Home.  The Upstairs bedrooms are good sized.  Over sized main floor bathroom could be an en-suite bedroom.  Formal Dining Room and a welcoming living area.  Fully fenced yard and extra parking at the rear of home.  Relax in the backyard and listen to the water feature and enjoy the warmth of the fire pit.
